msgid "SCM analytics (v0.5)"
msgstr "SCM 分析 (v0.5)"

#: ../../source/guide/scm-analytics.md:3
msgid ""
"A pandas-native analytics layer that turns every byte of your Anno save "
"into decision-ready tables. The analyzers line up with the question "
"*where is my bottleneck, and what do I do about it?*"
msgstr ""
"pandas ベースの分析層．Anno のセーブデータを意思決定に使える表に変換します．"
"各 analyzer は *ボトルネックはどこで，どう対処すべきか* という問いに"
"答えるように並んでいます．"

